descriptionHTML:
Neon Energy analog interactive watch face for Android wear.

Night city .. everyone gets a different color ... all in the light of the day seemed so gloomy and sad, revives .. streetlights, numerous neon signs, the stream of car headlights... life begins.

Features of the watch face:

- Date and day of weekly
- Second time
- Battery
- Weather
- Dual battery
- Color customization
- 2 Ambient modes
- Interactive mode (change color, open app, change dials)
- And other settings

-Weather information is provided by http://openweathermap.org

Compatible with:

- Android Wear devices
